LEO PRIME stepped off of his ship along with WINGCALIBER and SANTON, a
noxious cloud of greenish brown follwing behind them smelling of
rotten bean pod.

To the side of HYDRAS the large form of CRYOTEK was standing. Although
not as large as HYDRAS himself, he was still an imposing figure. He
wrinkled his nose as he looked over at LEO but said nothing.

Quickly steppeing off the ramp LEO looked at HYDRAS, "Wasn't it
suppose to be you who had the information?" He looked at the other
soldiers who were with HYDRAS, "You were going to locate where Dark
Rodimus had gone using that device?"

As LEO talked TORCA and NOCTORRO both stepped off the ship to look
around, followed quickly by BANTOR and AIRHAMMER, both of them looking
a little green, that smell seeming to have an affect on them as well.
One of them mumbling something about QUICKSTRIDE.
